OL,3,COne year after Assad fall Syria's
OL,4,Cdisplaced children dream of going home
OL,6,FA year after the ousting of Bashar al-
OL,7,FAssad, students in the country are
OL,8,Fstill getting used to a different life
OL,9,Ffor those who were displaced, ITV News
OL,10,FInternational Editor Emma Murphy
OL,11,Freports
OL,13,FOver the 13 years of Syria's civil
OL,14,Fwar, more than 12 million people were
OL,15,Fdisplaced, seven million within the
OL,16,Fcountry, five million beyond its
OL,17,Fborders.
