OL,3,COne year after Assad fall Syria's
OL,4,Cdisplaced children dream of going home
OL,6,FAs a result of the fall of former
OL,7,FPresident Bashar al-Assad, this year
OL,8,Fis the first time the children of Al-
OL,9,FAmal school have been able to learn in
OL,10,Frelative peace
OL,12,FAs Jihad Almahmoud, the head of the
OL,13,Fschool, explained: "In Syria, after
OL,14,Fthe liberation, one thing has changed:
OL,15,Fwe feel safer now. The sounds of war
OL,16,Fare finally over."
OL,18,FHe is clear on the importance of this
OL,19,Fhaven of learning for those whose
OL,20,Flives remain disrupted by the politics
OL,21,Fof their country.
